<font color="yellow">Ayah!</font>

549
00:48:48,100 --> 00:48:51,600
<font color="yellow">Ayah mengusir keluarga Jung Soon?</font>

550
00:48:51,600 --> 00:48:55,800
<font color="yellow">Tak usah berlebihan.
