553
00:49:02,300 --> 00:49:05,200
<font color="yellow">Kau tahu sendiri alasannya.</font>

554
00:49:05,200 --> 00:49:09,300
<font color="yellow">Aku mencintai Jung Soon!</font>

555
00:49:10,990 --> 00:49:13,390
<font color="yellow">Tapi sepertinya dia
