563
00:49:38,600 --> 00:49:40,490
<font color="yellow">Kau belum sadar juga?</font>

564
00:49:40,490 --> 00:49:45,390
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak perlu uang.</font>

565
00:49:48,990 --> 00:49:52,300
<font color="yellow">Kita lihat saja nanti.</font>

