568
00:50:45,600 --> 00:50:47,490
<font color="yellow">Sedang apa kau?</font>

569
00:50:51,390 --> 00:50:53,200
<font color="yellow">Kau tidak lihat?</font>

570
00:50:55,300 --> 00:50:56,390
<font color="yellow">Apa yang kau lakukan?</font>

571
00:50:56,390 --> 00:50:58,990
<font color="yellow">Pergi. Teman-temanku mau datang.</font>

572
00:50:58,990 --> 00:51:01,800
<font color="yellow">Temanmu?
