582
00:52:08,390 --> 00:52:10,300
<font color="yellow">Jawabanku adalah tidak.</font>

583
00:52:13,390 --> 00:52:15,490
<font color="yellow">Hubungan kita takkan berhasil.</font>

584
00:52:15,490 --> 00:52:16,890
<font color="yellow">Baiklah, tapi...</font>

585
00:52:18,300 --> 00:52:20,200
<font color="yellow">...pulanglah ke Kediaman Haneul.</font>

586
00:52:21,100 --> 00:52:23,100
<font color="yellow">Jika kau merasa tidak nyaman di sana,
