588
00:52:28,300 --> 00:52:29,800
<font color="yellow">Urusi urusanmu sendiri.</font>

589
00:52:29,800 --> 00:52:31,700
<font color="yellow">Aku akan mengurus diriku sendiri.</font>

590
00:52:32,490 --> 00:52:34,600
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau tidak mau
