593
00:52:42,490 --> 00:52:44,700
<font color="yellow">Aku bisa ke rumah pamanku saja.</font>

594
00:52:44,700 --> 00:52:46,200
<font color="yellow">Jangan bohong.</font>

595
00:52:46,800 --> 00:52:48,600
<font color="yellow">Apa kau mau
