00:56:33,700 --> 00:56:37,100
<font color="yellow">Benarkah?/
Ya.</font>

641
00:56:37,600 --> 00:56:41,600
<font color="yellow">Baiklah.
Syukurlah.</font>

642
00:56:44,800 --> 00:56:46,800
<font color="yellow">Ketua!
Kau baik-baik saja?</font>

643
00:56:46,800 --> 00:56:49,490
<font color="yellow">Aku baik-baik saja.
