00:57:26,490 --> 00:57:28,200
<font color="yellow">Kau datang rupanya.</font>

649
00:58:09,490 --> 00:58:10,990
<font color="yellow">Ibu.</font>

650
00:58:28,990 --> 00:58:35,490
<font color="yellow">Ibu... tinggal di Kediaman Haneul?</font>

